{"tid":642240,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搭地鐵返屋企遇到世界級港女","createTime":"2018-04-25T15:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T03:37:03.000Z","uid":17088,"like":2789,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f0337a2ac5bee872a2a6453fdd627dfb5cec88","tid":642240,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:25:53.000Z","msg":"情境似係啱啱同完男方家長食飯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  港女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢條仔<br />\n<br />\n: 你呀媽煮飯無味嘅<br />\n: 吓<br />\n: 咩調味料都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n: 年紀大要食得清淡嘛 下次上去我搵豉油辣醬俾你點啦<br />\n: 唉諗起遲吓幾十年成日要食啲無味既嘢就覺得慘<br />\n: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  -&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  -&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n: 你呀爸又懶好笑咁 啲gag得佢一個自己笑<br />\n: 老人家係咁架啦<br />\n: 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度我望住條仔呆咗咁企喺度<br />\n佢望住我無奈既眼神我就知道幾件事<br />\n1.  我幾時有話娶你?<br />\n2. 點解娶完你你旨意我呀媽煮俾你?<br />\n3. 有得你食仲嫌三嫌四 唔啱你煮囉<br />\n4. 嫌哂我全家你當你邊個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早飛早著啦巴打 呢條女一睇就知惡啃"},{"pid":"5c8e8272657fc93ceeb3c5aa1a23a2dcdb6dd636","tid":642240,"uid":64131,"like":16,"dislike":233,"score":-217,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"條女傲驕   鋪排幾十年果句姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c5485138b5888bc76dca2fa139906e779d3032","tid":642240,"uid":138138,"like":82,"dislike":16,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"條仔：其實我鍾意男人。。。"},{"pid":"468562b60b883c2e6bc5c4ba19cc53d35590fb99","tid":642240,"uid":76098,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"quo